_sText:
Here is an adaptation of an old map called woohoo2.
The original was mapped by my brother glougloup in March 2003 for cs 1.5 (or 1.3, i don't remember exactly).
since the original was very popular I thought i had to adapt to the source engine.
It is a simple map but fun map.
A closed universe with many breakables
No waiting time

Just try and enjoy.
